<h1 id=3D"id-08.SD:InterestandTaxSummary-Solution"><span>Solution</span></h=
1>
<h2 id=3D"id-08.SD:InterestandTaxSummary-SolutionOverview"><span>Solution O=
verview</span></h2>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>As a high-level overview, the solution enables the following capacities=
 in W1C which allows customers to:=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>view the tax and interest summary under their accounts for the latest t=
hree financial years, if the accounts are interest bearing.&nbsp;</li>
<li>view the tax and interest for the latest three financial years for a pa=
rticular account in the Account Activity page.&nbsp;</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Below is a breakdown of the scope and the responsible party for the cor=
responding scope of work.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table id=3D"TBL1773175605599" class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTa=
ble" style=3D"width: 71.0996%;">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col style=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 15.0294%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 34.8192%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 50.1581%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Frontend component</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Scope</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Responsible</th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Interest and tax Summary</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Create a new component "Account Utils API" wh=
ich is responsible for pagination, filtering and sorting on Account-level d=
ata.</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Account te=
am</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Interest and tax Summary / Account Activity</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Create =
a new INF API to:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">return data from the ATLAS Dynamo=
DB with Restful Endpoints.</span></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Account te=
am</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Interest and tax Summary</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Create =
a new EXP API to:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">return tax and interest data of t=
he latest three FY with the Account INF API.</span></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Channel team</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Account Activity</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Create =
a new EXP API to:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">return a summary of tax and inter=
est for the latest three financial years with the instl-account-transaction=
s-v1 API.</span></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Channel team</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Interest and tax Summary</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Do the account grouping in the UI which:</p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">triggers query calls to the Entit=
lement to return account grouping.</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">get a list of accounts from Entit=
lement with the selected account grouping.</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">triggers GTS interest detail INF =
API with accounts returned from Entitlement.&nbsp;</span></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Channel team</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Interest and tax Summary / Account Activity</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Defines AWS Glue Job to transforms and loads data from the 10X Kafka to=
 the Transaction Iceberg bucket.</li>
<li>Defines AWS Glue Job to transforms and loads data from the Transaction =
Iceberg bucket to the Interest and Tax Summary bucket and DynamoDB for Chan=
nel's consumption.</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">ATLAS team</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
