<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>API to get Account activity data=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>retrieve tax and interest summary for a single account in a given timef=
rame.=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>including information such as:=20
<ul>
<li>Interest Earned (credit_interest_paid)</li>
<li>Withholding Tax (debit_interest_charged )</li>
<li>Interest Received (calculated as- (wht_deducted - wht_refunded) )</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
